                    <span>Go ahead, take a tour of my house.  You will be able to tell which walls I did before I bought this book and which ones were done professionally after I bought it.  No question, if you are a mud-smearing homeowner like me and can't stand to pay someone to do it right, this book will help.  You still have to pay attention and do it just like he says. I'm very satisfied and can't stand it when people borrow my copy so they can see how to do drywall like me.</span>
                  
              
